    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Rhododendron mingii A. Flowing branch. B. Close-up view of leaf blade abaxial surface. C. Gynoecium. D. Stamens. E. Opened corolla. F. Habit. (A–E drawn by Y. Luo from the holotype)." ;
